lead_paragraph: Third-seeded Jelena Ostapenko of Latvia played Timea Babos for the first time, beating the seventh-seeded Hungarian 7-6 (3), 2-6, 6-3 on Friday to reach the semifinals of the Katowice Open.

headline.print_headline: Giorgi, Ostapenko, Cibulkova, Parmentier Advance in Katowice
